--------------------------------------------------------------------------------
INFORMATION
--------------------------------------------------------------------------------

This file lists changes made to the Ansible role. It follows semantic versioning
guidelines. The content is sorted in reverse chronological order and formatted
to allow easy grepping by scripts.

The fields are:
B: bug
C: change
E: enhancement
F: feature

--------------------------------------------------------------------------------

* Version 2.3.0 (2020-06-15)
F: Add dependency 'audispd_plugins'
F: Manage 'syslog.conf' file on CentOS 8
F: Activate syslog

* Version 2.2.0 (2019-10-14)
F: Add support for CentOS 8

* Version 2.1.0 (2019-05-26)
F: Port role to Ansible 2.8

* Version 2.0.1 (2019-02-15)
E: Remove obsolete comment parameter

* Version 2.0.0 (2019-02-13)
C: Redesign 'auditd_config_all' option (alter config variable to string)
C: Redesign 'auditd_config_group' option (alter config variable to string)
C: Redesign 'auditd_config_host' option (alter config variable to string)

* Version 1.0.0 (2018-12-13)
E: Mark Ansible role as 'stable'
E: Minor style improvement
E: Rename config parameters

* Version 0.3.0 (2018-05-21)
F: Port role to Ansible 2.5

* Version 0.2.1 (2018-04-24)
E: Simplify role by removing 'template' option

* Version 0.2.0 (2018-03-30)
F: Port role to Ansible 2.4

* Version 0.1.0 (2018-01-15)
F: Initial release
